Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
values{2} "iDet2D" DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE, `Простой` values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_SIMPLE, `Простой`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.`
if gs_cont_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=4 if line_cont_pen=0 then parameters line_cont_pen=4
if gs_fill_pen=0 then parameters gs_fill_pen=91 if runout_fill_pen=0 then parameters runout_fill_pen=91 if line_fill_pen=0 then parameters line_fill_pen=91
VALUES "A" RANGE (0,) VALUES "B" RANGE (0,) VALUES "rout_area_x" RANGE [0,) VALUES "rout_area_y" RANGE [0,)
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE THEN LOCK "goal","net_mat","goal_mat" ENDIF
IF iDet2D = DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED THEN LOCK "gs_dashed_line" ENDIF
IF iDet2D = DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE THEN LOCK "line_fill_pen" ENDIF
IF goal=0 THEN LOCK "net_mat","goal_mat" ENDIF
Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2
! const values for parameter: iDet2D DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE = 1 DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED = 2
